data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Welcome to your new home! This Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 full bathroom home with garage, is located on a cul-in the family friendly community at The Farm of Carolina Forest. The master bedroom suite has its own private bathroom, walk in closet, and is located on the ground floor, Additionally two other bedrooms, and a full size bathroom are located on the first floor. The fourth bedroom is a mother-in-law style suite with its own bathroom, and is located upstairs. This room could also be used for a bonus room, workout room, office area, or other endless possibilities! This home has been Beautifully landscaped and features a custom oversized paver patio with Edison lighting, perfect for grilling, fire pit and entertaining! This home is located on a Cul-De-Sac street with very low traffic. The Farm in Carolina Forest is a family friendly community with sidewalks and Amenities galore! This Community has neighborhood pools, playground, sports courts and recreation areas! Located in a highly desirable school district, near retail stores, grocery stores, restaurant, public library, and golf courses. Is a very short drive only minute's to the Beach front!! Conveniently located with easy access to Highway 31, Robert Grissom Parkway, 17 Bypass & Business, Hwy 90, 501 & 22. Centralized in between the north and south ends of Myrtle Beach. Prime location close to everything. **** BE SURE TO SEE VIRTUAL TOUR LINK BELOW! **** Won't last long!! Call to schedule a showing:
